ketai.ui

Class KetaiList

  • java.lang.Object
    • ListView
      • ketai.ui.KetaiList

  • public class KetaiList
extends ListView
    The KetaiList class provides an android UI scroll list. To receive the selection data a sketch should define the following method:

    void onKetaiListSelection(String selection) - selection is the string selected from the list
